# Input

```yml
# Ranking of 1998 home runs
---
- Mark McGwire
- Sammy Sosa
- Ken Griffey

# Team ranking
---
- Chicago Cubs
- St Louis Cardinals

```


# Error
```text
reformat: output mismatch
--- re-formatted
+++ formatted
@@ -4,6 +4,7 @@
 - Sammy Sosa
 - Ken Griffey
 
-# Team ranking---- Chicago Cubs
-- St Louis Cardinals # Team ranking---
+# Team ranking---
+- Chicago Cubs
+- St Louis Cardinals
 # Team ranking

IR differences:
--- re-formatted IR
+++ formatted IR
@@ -6,14 +6,12 @@
 - Sammy Sosa
 - Ken Griffey
 
-# Team ranking---",
-  line_suffix([" # Team ranking---"]),
+# Team ranking",
+  line_suffix([" # Team ranking"]),
   expand_parent,
-  verbatim([
-    "- Chicago Cubs
-- St Louis Cardinals"
-  ]),
-  line_suffix([hard_line_break, "# Team ranking"]),
-  expand_parent,
+  "---
+- Chicago Cubs
+- St Louis Cardinals
+",
   hard_line_break
 ]
\ No newline at end of file

```
